Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.15,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s have a White Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:08.10,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:10.69,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Just the five of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:11.65,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,How would we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.07,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:14.95,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find a way somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:17.95,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,...because we've just gotta sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.42,text,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Music Practice Room Two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:51.86,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Choir Club Culture Fair | Beauties and the Frogs \N Script - Miyamoto | - Wakana to coach everyone on their song parts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:53.30,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the best case scenario?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.30,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Choreography - Sawa | Set - Tanaka | Props - Wien \NCostumes - Wein? | Stage Crew - Everyone \N (17 days to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.13,Default,wak,0000,0000,0000,,That we get the school's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.17,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,And that people from \Nother clubs join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.27,Default,sana,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, a regular culture fair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where loads of people come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:05.10,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Then, worst case would be that \Nthe school doesn't allow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:08.02,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,And that we sing, alone, \Nin an empty gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:11.37,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,The worst would be if \Nwe can't sing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:12.69,Default,sana,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:17.19,Default,wak,0000,0000,0000,,But I’d still prefer to \Nhave a large audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:24.56,Default,wak,0000,0000,0000,,If we can sing this song together,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.95,Default,wak,0000,0000,0000,,we’ll think of each other \Nwhenever we hear it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:30.25,Default,wak,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how far we’re \Nscattered after graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.88,Default,wak,0000,0000,0000,,We'll remember being invited, \Nand arguing, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.42,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Getting mad, and laughing, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:38.36,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting, and losing, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.30,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Saying weird things, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.70,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting great friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:51.31,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,If a whole crowd of people \Nshare that fun memory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with us by listening to our song,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:58.06,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,remembering that would be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an encouragement to me, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:01.28,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.50,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then we’ve \Ngotta make this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.87,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's make it a \Nperformance to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:10.27,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pour everything into this song
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and step out into the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.92,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:15.27,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I the only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:21.47,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12 \NPiling Up and Rippling
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.59,Default,work,0000,0000,0000,,We're collecting the trash from \Nthe culture fair as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please deposit it by the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:29.23,Default,stu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:37.02,text,labels,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Defective Metronomes | Culture \NFair Props (Made by Maeda)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:47.25,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Okita!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.12,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:59.52,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Could I, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take your picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.05,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.80,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yeah, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.76,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.84,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hamachi... I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe this guy a picture of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for helping me paint the sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.93,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But you know what, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for even mentioning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:24.42,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.20,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.99,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,But make sure it’s flattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:30.91,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:33.48,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to take it from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.94,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Does it make a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.05,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.17,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.06,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.96,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the guy I'll have \Na horse stomp on him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the quality of his work is too low.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.86,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.39,Default,hama,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka, I’m impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:19.33,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.86,Default,hama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:24.38,Default,hama,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this line... It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.09,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd have a horse stomp \Non you if the quality sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.07,Default,hama,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn’t mind being \Nstomped on by her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.25,Default,hama,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:54.61,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,I think this part flows nicely, \Nbut it needs a bit more “oomph.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:56.12,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.21,Default,wak,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.08,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where’d Wien's props go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:01.96,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,They’re gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:03.75,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Would Konatsu have them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.21,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:08.43,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,In a meeting, so she \Nshouldn't have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:10.04,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I saw someone \Nwith them earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.41,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.84,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:35.93,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.91,Default,mats,0000,0000,0000,,As the White Festival’s been canceled,\Nany leftover budget
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,funds should be returned \Nto the school and—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:43.82,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.96,Default,mat,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.30,Default,kon,0000,0000,0000,,I propose a cancellation of the \Ncancellation of the White Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:52.05,Default,mats,0000,0000,0000,,The cancellation's already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.22,Default,kon,0000,0000,0000,,And you’re okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.75,Default,kon,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything about the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't you find it questionable \Nthat they canceled
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the fair just because \Nof some construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.06,Default,kon,0000,0000,0000,,We all put a lot of effort \Ninto getting ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.57,Default,kon,0000,0000,0000,,So many people were \Nlooking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.24,Default,kon,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this isn't a big deal for those
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who'll be in big competitions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.82,Default,kon,0000,0000,0000,,or pursuing professional careers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but some of us don’t have \Nany other stage to stand on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.80,Default,kon,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I don’t want to become
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the kind of sad adult who blindly \Nfollows wrong directions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.85,Default,kon,0000,0000,0000,,just because they came from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.55,Default,kon,0000,0000,0000,,At least let the student council
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,propose to keep the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:32.59,Default,hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There wouldn’t be enough time \Nfor our club to prepare a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:36.56,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,And you call {\i1}us {\i0}amateurs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.72,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so great, put your money \Nwhere your mouth is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.00,Default,mats,0000,0000,0000,,Order, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.79,Default,mats,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those in favor of the \Nchoir club's suggestion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please raise your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:55.01,Default,kaz,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t hurt to ask, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.62,Default,mat,0000,0000,0000,,Your proposal is denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:08.59,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! But we’re still gonna sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.40,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.88,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka, why didn't you \Nstop them right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:37.87,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.62,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're the club president! You \Nshould’ve taken better care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.21,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Why didn't anybody notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.21,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,But you saw it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.82,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Not clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.57,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether you get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.80,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:53.88,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sun will set, \Nmorning will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:58.39,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Each and every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.03,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.85,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be able to \Nfinish them all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.26,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.49,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.62,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry the student council \Nangle didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.84,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.45,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll just keep at it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:18.85,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.91,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Now let’s go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:36.18,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:39.14,Default,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are. Will that be all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.85,Default,wak,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:45.45,Default,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I left the flowers by the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.94,Default,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.52,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.61,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell Mom that \Nyou're hard at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:53.48,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:57.33,Default,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Bye. Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:58.99,Default,wom,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:09:59.95,Default,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.82,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,I haven’t been
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,able to create a single \Nlasting thing on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:26.56,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,The song we wrote together...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:29.73,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,The choir club we created... \NNothing I've done compares.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:35.75,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,That school was the only \Ntie to music I had left,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now even that’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.53,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,I guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the end, you were the \Nonly one the music loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:55.14,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.70,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Vice principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.93,text,grave,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sakai Family
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.93,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind listening to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.24,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,It's the song I wrote with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:18.66,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,The phrase you used for the \Nrefrain is a bit unconventional.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:23.82,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,But I can sense Mahiru in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:30.73,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to finish it thanks \Nto the advice you gave me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:33.14,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,that music should be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.34,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what Mahiru said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:42.05,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,She was constantly telling \Nme to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:46.67,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got no right to give advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:51.62,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,But for me, enjoying it wasn’t enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.04,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,The support of my friends \Nwas equally important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.26,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,They encouraged me \Nthrough my struggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:00.00,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,They're all so different from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:03.03,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,but they’re honest and determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.70,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,We fought, but we also worked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:10.15,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,I know my mother had a \Nfriend like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone to have fun with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone to share her worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I finished the song \Nwe promised to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m glad I could create this \Nsong with you and my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treasure it always, for \Nbringing us all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:11.39,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Konatsu's not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.34,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't had a morning \Nmeeting in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.25,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Was he here all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.03,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, morning, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.31,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.14,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna wear yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.58,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do the costumes after \NI finished the props, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.44,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.34,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to make costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.13,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll figure it out. I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:45.28,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,You're kinda clumsy, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.38,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all try to come \Nup with a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.23,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.90,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes down to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,draping these over us \Nmight look pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.77,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,So, Wakana, I was practicing \Nyesterday and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.52,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Have a little faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.28,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:19.45,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.04,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Could you teach me how to make these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:26.53,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,You? Have you ever sewn before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:29.80,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I know how to thread a needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.71,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,The sewing machine is backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:45.28,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys so set on \Nhaving the White Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:51.28,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, Miyamoto and \NSakai have their reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:54.12,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,but for me it's just \Nthat I like singing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.65,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,and I want to finish what I started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.82,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.06,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,All right, enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll break the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:08.22,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,No, please! I can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.22,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm offering \Nto do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:18.83,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.25,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make five \Ncostumes by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.95,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guys give me a hand over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.25,Default,all,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:31.66,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and get Kuwata from \Nclass 2 and Hara from class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.57,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,They'd be good to have on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.45,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.13,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,And get bean buns from the canteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:44.46,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.72,Default,kata,0000,0000,0000,,For everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:46.63,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.63,Default,naga,0000,0000,0000,,We'd very much like to \Ngrant your request,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.91,Default,naga,0000,0000,0000,,since you seem to have \Nyour heart set on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.29,Default,kita,0000,0000,0000,,But if the board,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean the school, decided \Nto cancel the fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:59.85,Default,kita,0000,0000,0000,,we're not sure we should be \Nadvertising it without their okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.85,Default,koya,0000,0000,0000,,It could cause serious problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:05.48,Default,shi,0000,0000,0000,,What did the board say to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:08.58,Default,nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:12.76,Default,nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, with what they're \Nplanning to build...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.77,Default,nag,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The region desperately needs the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:17.49,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.33,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I want as many people as \Npossible hear our song,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it's just one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.87,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do more than \Nadvertising at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.94,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If they're not interested in our song,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they don't have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.51,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe some of them would want to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be there to show their \Nsupport for our futures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:41.04,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I know there are some \Nthings I just have to let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:44.44,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think the culture \Nfair is one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:47.48,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It means so much to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.56,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.78,Default,hana,0000,0000,0000,,Putting up posters in our \Nshops should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:58.88,Default,naga,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a few graduates from \NShiro High live around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.41,Default,naga,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm sure they'd want \Nto stop by one last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before it's shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.64,Default,hana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.87,Default,naga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Were you a music major?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:10.05,Default,hana,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I was just a regular student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.84,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the music for \NSakai-san's song and a recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.50,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's still pretty rough,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll at least be \Nable to hear us sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:21.72,Default,ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:26.03,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I like the \Nway you play piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:28.48,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's gentle, yet strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.57,Default,ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.51,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do it, we'll \Njust record Wakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:37.57,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,But we'd prefer to have \Nyour accompaniment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.66,Default,hiro,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:42.37,Default,hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drag others into \Nyour personal whims,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the school's facing a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.75,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we be singing \N{\i1}because{\i0} there's a crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.65,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Hirohata-san, why do you sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:54.44,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,You're not planning to make \Na career of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:59.51,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,I may not like you, \Nbut I know you love singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:02.10,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,We did used to be in the same club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.85,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.35,Default,hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.98,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, sing with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.65,Default,hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.43,Default,hiro,0000,0000,0000,,As club president, I can't go off and do
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever I want, like {\i1}some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:21.10,Default,hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Go preach your childish "I love \Nsinging!" to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:23.87,Default,hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm way more serious \Nabout music than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:29.25,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm doing this on a whim?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.75,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet in the halls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.33,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:43.06,Default,hir,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:45.38,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,Begin practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:46.26,Default,hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.59,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,Ueno-san, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.12,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.31,Default,Ueno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:57.44,text,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}A Brighter Future For You
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:58.21,Default,princ,0000,0000,0000,,This might not be a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for students participating \Nin big competitions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:04.04,Default,princ,0000,0000,0000,,or pursuing professional careers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but some of them don't have \Nany other stage to stand on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:11.14,Default,boar,0000,0000,0000,,Do those students really need a stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.13,Default,princ,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.91,Default,princ,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:17.84,Default,princ,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to become \Nthe sad kind of adult
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who tramples my students' dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.40,Default,boar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this has been hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:27.21,Default,boar,0000,0000,0000,,Once it all blows over,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should celebrate with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.67,Default,boar,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you want to \Nstir up trouble now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when everything's been settled?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:38.33,Default,boar,0000,0000,0000,,I spotted this in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:43.87,text,post,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Final White Festival of Shirohamazaka High
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:43.87,text,post,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shirohamazaka High Choir \Nand Sometimes Badminton Club
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:43.42,Default,boar,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any unnecessary discord
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the locals over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:49.00,Default,boar,0000,0000,0000,,Construction is already \Nbehind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.70,Default,boar,0000,0000,0000,,Students are not to be on school grounds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,past 5 P.M. on school days,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and not at all on Sundays and holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.34,Default,boar,0000,0000,0000,,Violators will be suspended from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:03.18,Default,pric,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a bit harsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:07.03,Default,boar,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to worry about \Nare the construction delays,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:13.02,text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6} White Festival \NFinally Tomorrow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:10.61,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,The props and costumes are done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:12.57,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd finish the backdrops \Nby pulling an all-nighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:17.01,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Please, sun! Please, sun! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:19.67,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who comes to see \Nus in this downpour is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,worth their weight in gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:23.39,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a rain whisperer, Konatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:28.11,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We've done all we could!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:29.99,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}It will soon be 5 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}All students must return \Nto their homes immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:33.89,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.59,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Even if nobody comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:39.40,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,My dad will be there, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:42.58,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,After all we've done, \Nif only one person shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:43.69,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,...it'd look pretty pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:45.70,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:48.32,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things were \Nout of our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:51.26,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,But it was still fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:25.91,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,Think it'll stop if we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:26.71,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:28.39,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You expected too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.39,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,But Konatsu's a rain whisperer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:30.30,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,There's no rain that won't end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:33.82,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:35.19,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,Right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:36.64,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit, ribbit, ribbit, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:40.29,Default,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Final Episode \NSunny Days and Crying and Sometimes Singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:37.99,Default,kona,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Sawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:40.31,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it, even if you \Nwon't acknowledge it.
